      "instruction": {
        "type": "static_text",
        "text": "Thank you so much for requesting a demo of Ubie's Smart Support system. \n\nHi, my name is Bea. \n\nI can be fully customized to \"answer overflow at peak times\", \"book appointments\", \"handle billing questions\" and more, for medical practices just like yours. \n\nCan I show you how the system works?"
