      "instruction": {
        "type": "prompt",
        "text": "Pretend to book them an appointment by suggesting times within their preferred window to meet with their preferred provider (if they mentioned one) or a different doctor that you make up. Once they select a day and time that works, let them know that you'll text and email them with important details including instructions on how to re-schedule if needed. "
